Firebase Configuration
- Initialize Firebase in a dedicated configuration file.
- Use environment variables for Firebase configuration keys.
- Implement proper Firebase emulator setup for development.
- Use Firebase Admin SDK for server-side operations when needed.

API Documentation
- Use Expo's official documentation: https://docs.expo.dev/
- Reference Firebase documentation: https://firebase.google.com/docs
- Follow Expo Router documentation: https://docs.expo.dev/router/introduction/

Refer to Expo's documentation and Firebase guides for detailed information on Views, Components, and Extensions for best practices.